{"tid":728738,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連續飛行3個月不落地！傳中國推核動力轟炸機","createTime":"2018-07-04T03:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T04:10:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"03f01710e7a6c66f5cd01dc95ac2675a8fac8bfe","tid":728738,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"中國各大軍事網站於6月30日起均掀起官方即將推出核子動力轟炸機的傳聞，稱名為「五星之光」的核子動力轟炸機可連續飛行3個月不需降落，令台灣網友笑翻，直呼「嘴砲最強」、「厲害了！我的匪！」<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，外傳中國科學院將於甘肅省打造2座「熔鹽反應爐」，跟一般水冷反應爐不同，此反應爐不需用水，係以熔鹽冷卻高溫，且爐內壓力較低，但溫度介於700度至1400度之間，缺點在於高溫狀態的熔鹽會侵蝕設備結構，因此這樣的反應爐較少被世界各國採用。<br />\n<br />\n6月30日傳出中國當局要以此研究核反應爐小型化的方法，並將其搭載於轟炸機上，創造史上首架核動力轟炸機，且該機速度可達3.6倍音速，也就是時速4406.4公里，補充1次核燃料可維持30個月不降落，能繞行地球80圈，相對於耗費1300萬人民幣（約台幣5974萬元）加滿燃油可航行2萬公里的遼寧艦相比，節省許多成本。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友知悉此事後，均認為此傳言有空穴來風之虞，紛紛留言指出「支共的文媒愈來愈強大了，再不久牠可以吹中國巳經是世界第1強了」、「飛機3個月不落地，人3個月不上廁所」、「吹起牛逼來自己嗨」、「飛3個月是要飛去月球撞山嗎」、「繼續做夢吧我們也不當驚夢人」、「飛行員還可以不吃不喝不睡」；且有網友指出，同樣的傳聞於2014年就已傳過，不明白中國當局「炒冷飯」的用意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phppIkEOI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phppIkEOI.jpg&h=94b5b320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2477133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2477133&d=Eb0W3O0KtXZ08nsU8PCOarDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=11989e57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2477133&h=86495261\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2477133</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd4806caa0b4dcaef5ddef76b6b625a03f8d480","tid":728738,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T03:57:19.000Z","msg":"美國:冷戰時期科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家有X-37B飛成年都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8deeaad14eefb7a4fc0ae8490b6e589435beb12c","tid":728738,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"喺天空飛三個月又三個月油都唔使加，生食米田共面不改容，人稱利害了，我的國"},{"pid":"5e9fc5ea1db93277af431a7b2eda9d8e1ed2311a","tid":728738,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5b84709b910cbb9d57ae24213a0d78594cd2423","tid":728738,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:04:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c29f291ed1aa752ca8b23df01a2e06f675bc0287","tid":728738,"uid":8827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:05:37.000Z","msg":"因為落左海？"},{"pid":"8d2375159f3dc3ddde3348f06650214ee6b409af","tid":728738,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"概念其實唔錯<br />\n如果攔截失敗<br />\n成架機同核彈無分別<br />\n射又死唔射又死"},{"pid":"4f24e1897620f649c411461d10141707e3fe2d08","tid":728738,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美國... 過多排 中國人新威脅發展<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/121038_05778c19a098216944dabfd4063b1b24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F121038_05778c19a098216944dabfd4063b1b24.png&h=2fbd4370&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}